COMMS: FLASH TRAFFIC — COMSTRIKFLTLANT TO TASK GROUP BRAVO.
COMMS: Soviet surface action group detected bearing three-four-zero, range one hundred twenty nautical miles. One Kirov-class. Two Udaloy escorts.
INTEL: This group broke from the main formation six hours ago. They are headed directly for the convoy lanes. Assessment: offensive sweep.
COMMS: Your task group will intercept and engage. Two Spruance-class destroyers. You have the firepower. Use it.
COMMS: Be advised: the Kirov carries P-700 Granit missiles. Mach two-point-five. Your CIWS will have seconds to react. Do not let them shoot first.
COMMS: COMMS out.
